  "instructions": [
    "Heat olive oil in a large skillet over medium heat.",
    "Add falafel and cook until golden brown, about 5 minutes.",
    "Stir-fry red bell peppers and green peppers for another 3-4 minutes.",
    "Add garlic to the skillet and sauté for an additional minute.",
    "Combine tomato paste with tangy sauce and pour over stir-fried vegetables and falafel.",
    "Mix well until all ingredients are coated in the sauce, adjusting seasoning as needed.",
    "Serve hot or at room temperature."
